      <title>美林证券和 Harvest Volatility Management 将支付 930 万美元以和解美国证券交易委员会的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/merrill-lynch-harvest-volatility-management-pay-93-mln-settle-sec-charges-2024-09-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美林证券、皮尔斯芬纳和史密斯公司和 Harvest Volatility Management LLC 已同意支付总计 930 万美元，以解决美国证券交易委员会与投资限制和费用相关的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/merrill-lynch-harvest-volatility-management-pay-93-mln-settle-sec-charges-2024-09-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 14:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
